Package: spacom
Type: Package
Title: Spatially weighted context data for multilevel modelling
Version: 0.9-3
Date: 2011-11-27
Author: Till Junge <till.junge@unil.ch>, Sandra Penic <sandra.penic@unil.ch>, Guy Elcheroth <guy.elcheroth@unil.ch>
Maintainer: Till Junge <till.junge@unil.ch>
Description: Constructs and describes spatially weighted context data from micro-level survey data by aggregation or from precise contextual indicators. Performs multilevel analyses where spatially weighted context data are combined with individual level predictor and outcome variables. Computes robust point estimates and standard errors by stratified resampling. Provides estimates of explained spatial dependency. 
License: GPL (>= 2)
LazyLoad: yes
Depends: methods, R (>= 2.10-0), spdep, foreach, lme4
Packaged: 2011-12-11 22:16:39 UTC; junge
Repository: CRAN
Date/Publication: 2011-12-12 07:15:34
